resources.string: Ibhethri lakho selifinyelele umjikelezo wokushaja wama-375. Ngenxa yokuthi kungase kube nenkinga yokushisa ngokweqile kwebhethri, lapho ibhethri yakho lifinyelela umjikelezo wokushaja wama-400 womthamo webhethri futhi isivinini sokushaja sizoncipha futhi kunconywa ukuba kushintshwe ibhethri. Okungakhethwa kukho kosekelo kuyatholakala, vakashela okuthi <u>g.co/pixel/6abattery</u> ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe.

Ngenxa yokuthi kungenzeka kube nenkinga yokushisa ngokweqile kwebhethri, umthamo webhethri kanye nesivinini sokushaja zincishisiwe, futhi kunconywa ukuba kushintshwe ibhethri. Okungakhethwa kukho kosekelo kuyatholakala, vakashela okuthi <u>g.co/pixel/6abattery</u> ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe.
